{"metadata":{"title":"Vector Tile Sources","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"abstract":[{"text":"Add and style a vector tile source","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/DDSCircleLayerExample","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Styling and Dynamic Data","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnimatedLineExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/WebAPIDataExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/LineStyleLayerExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/POIAlongRouteExample","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/GeoJSON","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/PMTiles"]}],"kind":"article","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This example uses UIKit"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This example shows how a vector data source can be added and a style for it can be configured dynamically.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The tiles are ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/demotiles\/tree\/gh-pages\/tiles-omt"},{"text":" that use the OpenMapTiles schema. We are interested in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/openmaptiles.org\/schema\/#poi"},{"text":" that are in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"poi","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" layer, and filter this further with an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSPredicate"},{"text":" to only show POIs with a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"class"},{"type":"text","text":" of shop. Each POI has a "},{"code":"rank","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" which is normally used to reduce label density. In this example, we use it to demonstrate how a numeric attribute can be used for styling with the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/maplibre.org\/maplibre-style-spec\/expressions\/#step"},{"type":"text","text":" expression. POIs with a rank between 0 and 10 get a red color, between 10 and 20 green, etc."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class DDSCircleLayerExample: UIViewController, MLNMapViewDelegate {","    var mapView: MLNMapView!","","    override func viewDidLoad() {","        super.viewDidLoad()","","        mapView = MLNMapView(frame: view.bounds, styleURL: AMERICANA_STYLE)","        mapView.autoresizingMask = [.flexibleWidth, .flexibleHeight]","        mapView.tintColor = .darkGray","","        \/\/ Set the mapâ€™s center coordinate and zoom level.","        let innsbruck = CLLocationCoordinate2D(latitude: 47.26497, longitude: 11.4088)","        mapView.setCenter(innsbruck, animated: false)","        mapView.zoomLevel = 14","","        mapView.delegate = self","        view.addSubview(mapView)","    }","","    \/\/ Wait until the style is loaded before modifying the map style.","    func mapView(_: MLNMapView, didFinishLoading style: MLNStyle) {","        let source = MLNVectorTileSource(identifier: \"demotiles\", configurationURL: URL(string: \"https:\/\/demotiles.maplibre.org\/tiles-omt\/tiles.json\")!)","","        style.addSource(source)","","        let layer = MLNCircleStyleLayer(identifier: \"poi-shop-style\", source: source)","","        layer.sourceLayerIdentifier = \"poi\"","        layer.predicate = NSPredicate(format: \"class == %@\", \"shop\")","","        \/\/ Style the circle layer color based on the rank","        layer.circleColor = NSExpression(mglJSONObject: [\"step\", [\"get\", \"rank\"], 0, \"red\", 10, \"green\", 20, \"blue\", 30, \"purple\", 40, \"yellow\"] as [Any])","        layer.circleRadius = NSExpression(forConstantValue: 3)","","        style.addLayer(layer)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"DDSCircleLayerExample.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Map data from OpenStreetMap. Style uses OpenMapTiles."}]}]}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/ddscirclelayerexample"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/WebAPIDataExample":{"abstract":[{"text":"Showing data from an API with custom styling and interaction","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/WebAPIDataExample","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/webapidataexample","kind":"article","role":"article","title":"Showing data from an API","type":"topic"},"DDSCircleLayerExample.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"DDSCircleLayerExample.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/DDSCircleLayerExample@2x.png","traits":["2x","light"]}],"alt":null},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/LineStyleLayerExample":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Adding an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to the map using a GeoJSON file.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/LineStyleLayerExample","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/linestylelayerexample","kind":"article","role":"article","title":"Using GeoJSON with a line style layer","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and